titles.title: Directing the Secretary of the Senate to make technical corrections in the enrollment of S. 1374.

action.text: Mr. Walden asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Received in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 9/12/2000--Introduced. Directs the Secretary of the Senate to make technical corrections in the enrollment of S. 1374 (development of a multi-agency campus project in Jackson, Wyoming).
